 I believe the meaning of life is to find purpose and fulfillment. In my opinion, life is not just about existing or surviving, but about living a life that has meaning and significance.
To find purpose and fulfillment, one must first understand themselves and their values. What are your passions and interests? What do you stand for, and what do you believe in? These questions can help you identify your core values and goals, which can serve as a guide for making decisions and setting priorities.
